	<div class="pricing-faq">
	
		<div class="pricing-faq-left">
			<h1>You're in control</h1>			
			<p>All plans are billed monthly and can be cancelled, upgraded or downgraded at any time. No contract and no setup fees. Save yourself just one hour of tedious work per month and HayPista pays for itself.</p>
			
			<h1>Do I have to pay during the off-season?</h1>
			<p>Nope! Just switch your team site to the Free Plan during the off season. You don't pay anything but still have all your team data 100% saved. When a new season starts, you just reactivate your team and are ready to roll. (Not applicable to Annual Plans.)</p>
			
			<h1>Does every player on the team have to pay?</h1>
			<p>Nope. There's a flat monthly charge for the entire team (paid by the "Team Manager").</p>
			
			<h1>What payment methods do you accept?</h1>
			<p>We currently accept Visa, Mastercard, PayPal and IBN Transfers.</p>
		</div>

