			<h1>How does the Free Plan work?</h1>
			<p>You can use the Free Plan as long as you like. There is no time limit and there are no hidden costs.</p>

			<h1>Can I cancel at any time?</h1>
			<p>Of course.</p>

			<h1>What web browsers work with HayPista?</h1>
